Project Bureau — ATF1502AS Logic Block B

Project Bureau aims at documenting the bitstream format of Microchip ATF15xx CPLDs. This is a work in progress.

Macrocell Configuration Bitmap

Logic block B uses 480 fuses at 15840..16320 for macrocells MC17, MC18, MC19, MC20, MC21, MC22, MC23, MC24, MC25, MC26, MC27, MC28, MC29, MC30, MC31, MC32.
